data.description: Welcome home!  This 2 bedroom, 2 ½ bathroom home with a second-floor bonus room/loft in a highly desirable gated community is perfect for the Florida lifestyle.  It is located near I75, shopping centers/malls, hospitals, and golf courses. Built in 2018 this home is still basically new and is move-in ready!  The spacious master suite has its own bathroom with dual sinks and a walk-in closet.    The kitchen is a must see with walnut cabinets, granite counter tops and matching appliances.  All major appliances stay to include the washer/dryer.    The second-floor bonus room/loft is great for a reading, TV, office work, and a playroom.  You choose. This home is current protected with an installed alarm system by guardian protection. The community has two pools, one in the townhome area a very short walk from the unit.  The other is at the club house which is a resort style pool.  The club house also boasts an exercise room, water play area and a covered outdoor lounge with a TV.  Don’t let this one pass you by!
